{"tid":1255714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁啟智：二十國集團駐港機構位置圖","createTime":"2019-06-24T15:25:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T15:28:47.000Z","uid":52609,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c5ffcbb5d4b6ca1c5dee9fdcca53f4d0a8b14ce5","tid":1255714,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T15:25:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/64949714_2256488684388455_5211803815669399552_o.png?_nc_cat=100&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=2ab9744a97efb00f6ece65b59a7b648d&amp;oe=5DC2C49E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F64949714_2256488684388455_5211803815669399552_o.png%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D2ab9744a97efb00f6ece65b59a7b648d%26oe%3D5DC2C49E&h=d028ef29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據瞭解，有網友計畫短期內拜訪世界各國駐港機構，這兒提供地圖一張以作參考。<br />\n<br />\n注意按照《維也納外交關係公約》，各使館處所和相關人員享有特殊地位，當地政府有責任保護。各位網友拜訪前最好先和對方約好，以免本地政府有所誤會引發不便。個別國家的使節可能不習慣接待網友拜訪，請時刻謹記保持友善尊重。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kaichil/photos/a.594779517226055/2256488681055122/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkaichil%2Fphotos%2Fa.594779517226055%2F2256488681055122%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=%2Fh6QBFvJ2171tI4HayrYRje9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=41f6c21e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kaichil/photos/a.594779517226055/2256488681055122/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"84ba196b81f945c2eb0b86a27548e1d32c64316e","tid":1255714,"uid":35842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T15:27:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Za9XbJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Za9XbJ.png&h=03a25356&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ZUZzYq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ZUZzYq.png&h=552a1c86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />